plot: The film follows five students as the world around them is transformed into chaos from an unexplained airborne plague of infection that turns their classmates into primal and bloodthirsty horrors. The five fight their through dorks, weirdo's and the school principal trying to get out alive, finally they find the A/V clubs video camera and barricade themselves into the school theater.
